der.com%2Ffinancial-conflicts-congress-members-rated-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econgressional%20insider%20trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Though%20in%20its%20infancy%2C%20the%20program%20could%20be%20a%20revolutionary%20way%20for%20journalists%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20the%20general%20public%20to%20hold%20public%20officials%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20Fall%202023%20master's%20capstone%20project%20at%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20Mats%20Dodd%2C%20Aditya%20Shah%2C%20Jocelyn%20Thai%2C%20and%20Connor%20Yen%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20PoliWatch%20to%20see%20if%20insider%20trading%20is%20as%20prevalent%20of%20an%20issue%20in%20Congress%20as%20many%20perceive%20it%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20dug%20into%20it%20and%20were%20really%20disappointed%20when%20we%20found%20that%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20there's%20maybe%20been%20twelve%20successful%20investigations%20that%20have%20led%20to%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Dodd%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20he%20believes%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcongress-stock-act-violations-penalties-consequences-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econgressional%20ethics%20committees%3C%2Fa%3E%20tend%20to%20sweep%20infractions%20%26quot%3Bunder%20the%20rug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20explained%20that%20PoliWatch%20works%20by%20feeding%20its%20system%20publicly%20available%20congressional%20stock%20filings%2C%20hearing%20schedules%2C%20committee%20assignments%2C%20and%20sponsored%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20basically%20contextualizing%20stock%20transactions%20with%20key%20information%20such%20as%20committee%20assignments%20sponsored%20legislation%20and%20our%20team%20of%20investigative%20experts%20to%20identify%20suspicious%20activities%20with%20ease%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20tool%20was%20already%20able%20to%20identify%20when%20lawmakers%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-bought-sold-covid-19-related-stocks-during-pandemic-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equestionable%20COVID-related%3C%2Fa%3E%20trades%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20investigated%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221614%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20a%20dashboard%20with%20congressional%20stock%20trading%20information%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660c315f1caec1275a6bee97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22988%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20front-facing%20dashboard%20of%20PoliWatch.%3Cp%3EPoliWatch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20see%20this%20tool%20as%20almost%20being%20like%20putting%20a%20magnifying%20glass%20on%20what's%20happening%20and%20letting%20the%20people%20see%20what's%20actually%20going%20on%20because%20it's%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20Dodd%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Maguire%2C%20the%20research%20director%20at%20Citizens%20for%20Responsibility%20and%20Ethics%20in%20Washington%2C%20is%20thrilled%20about%20the%20new%20tool's%20potential%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20understanding%20correctly%20with%20this%20can%20do%2C%20it%20is%20going%20to%20potentially%20revolutionize%20the%20public%20and%20journalist's%20ability%20to%20track%20the%20stock%20trades%20and%20ownership%20of%20members%20of%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoliWatch%20is%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bprivate%20beta%26quot%3B%20period%20as%20the%20project%20lacks%20outside%20financial%20support.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20keeping%20it%20up%20and%20online%20costs%20the%20team%20around%20%24500%20a%20month.%20Shah%20said%20the%20team%20still%20plans%20to%20update%20and%20improve%20the%20product%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20anyone's%20full-time%20job%20%E2%80%94%20they%20haven't%20even%20incorporated%20a%20business%20yet%20for%20PoliWatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20the%20project%20isn't%20publicly%20available%20yet%20is%20how%20young%20it%20is.%20Dodd%20said%20that%20for%20now%2C%20the%20team%20wants%20%26quot%3Ba%20human%20in%20the%20loop%20in%20any%20outputs%20of%20our%20model%20because%20we%20want%20people%20with%20expertise%20in%20this%20area%20to%20vet%20information%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20have%20the%20data%20misconstrued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShah%20added%20that%20looking%20ahead%2C%20they'd%20like%20to%20expand%20PoliWatch's%20reach%20beyond%20congressional%20transactions%20to%20promote%20corporate%20accountability%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECongress'%20thorny%20trading%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider's%20far-reaching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconflicted-congress-key-findings-stock-act-finances-investing-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BConflicted%20Congress%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20investigation%20found%20in%202021%2C%20lawmakers%20regularly%20violate%20the%20federal%20Stop%20Trading%20on%20Congressional%20Knowledge%20(STOCK)%20Act%20with%20little%20consequence.%20Many%20members%20of%20Congress%20own%20shares%20of%20companies%20that%20overlap%20with%20their%20committee%20assignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublic%20sentiment%20toward%20members%20of%20Congress%20and%20their%20families%20trading%20stocks%20came%20to%20a%20head%20at%20the%20end%20of%202021%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-are-free-market-economy-pelosi-rejects-stock-ban-congress-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethen-Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20Nancy%20Pelosi%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20out%20against%20banning%20the%20practice%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pelosi%20standing%20at%20a%20microphone%20and%20answering%20questions%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660c3a4a1caec1275a6bfa28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20hei