ners%20Have%20No%20Right%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Bail%20Hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Farvind-kejriwal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20traded%20sharp%20barbs%20and%20hard-nosed%20legal%20arguments%20in%20equal%20measure%20Wednesday%2C%20as%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20heard%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20boss'%20plea%20for%20interim%20relief.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20last%20month%20-%20and%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20national%20capital's%20Tihar%20Jail%20till%20April%2015%20-%20for%20his%20role%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bkingpin%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20alleged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-scam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliquor%20policy%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20arguments%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20representing%20the%20ED%2C%20issued%20a%20strong%20rejoinder%20to%20arguments%20about%20the%20timing%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20declaring%20%26quot%3Bcriminals%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20arrested%20and%20put%20in%20jail%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BUnder-trial%20prisoners%20have%20no%20right%20to%20say%2C%20'we%20will%20commit%20a%20crime%20and%20we%20will%20not%20be%20arrested%20because%20elections%20are%20here'.%20This%20is%20completely%20ridiculous%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raju%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20began%20his%20argument%20by%20claiming%20%26quot%3Bsole%20purpose%20of%20the%20arrest%20(of%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister)%20is%20to%20humiliate...%20incapacitate%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20the%20only%20real%20challenger%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20Delhi's%20seven%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEfforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20break%20AAP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20ED%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20have%20any%20evidence%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20sitting%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20unwarranted%2C%20particularly%20before%20an%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-news-delhi-liquor-policy-case-kejriwal-produced-in-court-probe-agency-may-seek-10-day-custody-5289012%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20on%20March%2021%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20after%20the%20High%20Court%20refused%20protection%20-%20has%20roiled%20his%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc.%20The%20opposition%20has%20accused%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20conspiracy%26quot%3B'%20i.e.%2C%20of%20using%20central%20investigative%20agencies%2C%20like%20the%20ED%2C%20to%20target%20political%20rivals%20before%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuppose%20a%20political%20person%20commits%20a%20murder%20before%20the%20election.%20Will%20he%20not%20be%20arrested%3F%20Will%20his%20arrest%20harm%20(the%20election)%3F%20You%20commit%20a%20murder%20and%20say%20I%20cannot%20be%20arrested%20because%20it%20will%20violate...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raju%20declared%2C%20trying%20to%20draw%20a%20parallel%20to%20the%20corruption%20charges%20against%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20-%20which%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20earlier%20said%20had%20no%20real%20evidence%20of%20his%20involvement%2C%20much%20less%20his%20central%20role%20in%20the%20alleged%20scam%20-%20also%20insisted%20%26quot%3Ba%20money%20trail%20is%20there...%20we%20have%20traced%20the%20money%20trail%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20further%20waved%20away%20claims%20by%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20that%20his%20arrest%2C%20and%20those%20of%20his%20colleagues%2C%20including%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20was%20largely%20based%20on%20statements%20by%20accused-turned-approvers%20(or%20government%20witnesses).%20The%20AAP%20has%20pointed%20to%20a%20pattern%20-%20the%20first%20of%20multiple%20statements%20provided%20by%20each%20former%20accused%20does%20not%20name%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20or%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20only%20after%20arrest%20and%20questioning%20that%20statements%20are%20changed%2C%20the%20AAP%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%20-%20which%20question%20was%20also%20posed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20it%20gave%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20bail%20-%20Mr%20Raju%20argued%20accused%20persons%20may%20change%20their%20statement%20after%20being%20presented%20with%20evidence.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20accused%20is%20confronted%20with%20material%20(then)%20they%20say%20'I%20was%20wrong'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20avoid%20statements%20and%20say%2C%20'No%2C%20no...%20these%20cannot%20be%20trusted.%20Cash%20payment%20was%20made...%20cash%20that%20was%20not%20accounted%20for.%20Source%20of%20the%20cash%20was%20a%20bribe...%20it%20could%20be%20Rs%20100%20crore%20or%20a%20little%20less%20than%20that.%20This%20has%20been%20accepted%20by%20the%20AAP%20candidate%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20WhatsApp%20chats%20and%20statements%20of%20hawala%20operators.%20We%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20data...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20pushback%20to%20arguments%20by%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20lawyer%2C%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20the%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20insisted%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20involved%20in%20all%20of%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EArvind%20Kejriwal's%20Bail%20Argument%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20earlier%20argued%20the%20ED%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20have%20any%20evidence%26quot%3B%20and%20that%