marks%20against%20INDIA%20ally%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%2C%20over%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%20The%20proposal%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20would%20be%20sent%20across%20to%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20party's%20disciplinary%20committee%20will%20take%20the%20final%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20state%20Congress%20committee%2C%20which%20has%20also%20decided%20to%20push%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20Mr%20Nirupam%20from%20the%20party's%20list%20of%20star%20campaigners%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20MP%20of%20both%20the%20House%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Mr%20Nirupam%20has%20been%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20ever%20since%20it%20named%20its%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20Upset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bone%20of%20contention%20is%20the%20Mumbai%20North-West%20seat%20-%20Mr%20Nirupam%20wants%20to%20contest%20the%20seat%2C%20but%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20has%20announced%20Amol%20Kirtikar%20as%20its%20candidate.%20The%20seat%20is%20currently%20held%20by%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Gajanan%20Kirtikar%2C%20who%20defeated%20Mr%20Nirupam%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20Gajanan%20Kirtikar%20sided%20with%20Eknath%20Shinde%20after%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20split.%20In%20a%20sharp%20move%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20fielded%20his%20son%20Amol%20from%20the%20seat.%20Gajanan%20Kirtikar%20has%20now%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20contest%20against%20his%20son.%20The%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20wants%20to%20field%20its%20candidate%20there%20as%20part%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20understanding%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVerbal%20Attacks%20On%20Ally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam%20has%20said%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20should%20not%20allow%20itself%20to%20be%20arm-twisted%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20party.%20Soon%20after%20the%20Sena%20list%20was%20out%2C%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20should%20not%20come%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20as%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20is%20not%20capable%20of%20winning%20any%20seat%20without%20Congress%20support.%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20arm-twisted%20the%20Congress%20to%20take%20five%20of%20the%20six%20seats%20in%20Mumbai.%20But%20the%20Congress%20should%20not%20allow%20itself%20to%20be%20arm-twisted%20like%20this.%20This%20action%20is%20against%20the%20Congress%20and%20it's%20a%20ploy%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20party%20in%20the%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam%20also%20alleged%20that%20Sena's%20candidate%20Amol%20Kirtikar%20took%20bribes%20during%20a%20free%20food%20initiative%20for%20migrant%20labourers%20during%20Covid%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Khichdi%20Scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20personal%20attack%20on%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbachi%20khuchi%20Shiv%20Sena%20pramukh%26quot%3B%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20split%20in%20his%20party%20after%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20mutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20Switching%20Parties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam%20has%20dropped%20broad%20hints%20over%20his%20next%20step.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20former%20Mumbai%20Congress%20chief%20said%20he%20is%20waiting%20for%20the%20high%20command%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20over%20the%20issues%20he%20has%20raised%20and%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20options%20are%20open%20for%20me%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20BJP%20president%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%20has%20said%20that%20people%20like%20Mr%20Nirupam%20are%20%26quot%3Balways%20welcome%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20party%20if%20he%20is%20ready%20and%20his%20thoughts%20align%20with%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20the%20political%20tenure%20of%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%2C%20he%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20for%20connecting%20people%20with%20Congress.%20He%20is%20well-recognised%20in%20North%20India.%20Talks%20with%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20have%20not%20happened%20yet%2C%20but%20if%20he%20is%20ready%20and%20his%20thoughts%20align%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20then%20people%20like%20him%20are%20always%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20not%20alone.%20The%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%20has%20also%20sent%20out%20feelers.%20Sena%20MLA%20Sanjay%20Shirsat%20has%20said%20Mr%20Nirupam%20will%20definitely%20be%20welcomed%20if%20he%20decides%20to%20leave%20Congress%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanjay%20Nirupam%20is%20very%20angry%20with%20Congress.%20If%20he%20wants%20to%20join%20us%2C%20we%20welcome%20him.%20However%2C%20the%20final%20decision%20in%20this%20regard%20lies%20with%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shirsat%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712141820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fp60k32jo_sanjay-nirupam_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsanjay-nirupam-maharashtra-congress-congress-to-expel-sanjay-nirupam-sources-say-proposal-in-the-works-5366509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Maharashtra%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20prepping%20a%20proposal%20to%20expel%20party%20leader%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20for%20his%20recent%20remarks%20against%20INDIA%20ally%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%2C%20over%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20according%20to%20sources%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsanjay-nirupam-maharashtra-congress-congress-to-expel-sanjay-nirupam-sources-say-proposal-in-the-works-5366509%22%2C%22cdnAmpU