0medals%20at%20the%202010%20edition%20of%20the%20Games%20as%20well%20as%20the%202009%20World%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20party%20General%20Secretary%20Vinod%20Tawde%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20boxer%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20a%20%3Cem%3Eghar%20wapsi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(homecoming)%20for%20me.%20I%20had%20contested%20the%20elections%20in%202019.%20It%20is%20good%20to%20be%20back.%20The%20way%20sportspersons%20are%20getting%20respect%20in%20the%20country%20and%20abroad%20now%20is%20commendable.%20When%20we%20used%20to%20go%20abroad%20to%20fight%20earlier%2C%20to%20the%20UK%20and%20Dubai%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20certain%20things%20would%20happen%20at%20the%20airports%20sometimes.%20But%20since%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20(Narendra)%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20we%20can%20go%20anywhere%20easily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20respect%20that%20sportspersons%20get%20under%20this%20government.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20government%2C%20help%20people%20and%20show%20them%20the%20right%20path.%20I%20am%20the%20same%20Vijender%20that%20I%20was%20and%20will%20call%20a%20spade%20a%20spade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijender%20Singh%20had%20backed%20wrestlers%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20in%20their%20protest%20against%20BJP%20MP%20and%20then%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20over%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20last%20year.%20When%20Sakshi%20Malik%20had%20announced%20her%20retirement%20from%20wrestling%20after%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20BJP%20MP%20had%20won%20the%20subsequent%20WFI%20elections%2C%20the%20boxer%20had%20called%20it%20a%20black%20day%20in%20the%20history%20of%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20questioned%20the%20silence%20of%20Indian