%20Ventura%20versions%20prior%20to%2013.6.6%2C%20Apple%20macOS%20Sonoma%20versions%20prior%20to%2014.4.1%2C%20Apple%20visionOS%20versions%20prior%20to%201.1.1%2C%20Apple%20iOS%20and%20iPadOS%20versions%20prior%20to%2017.4.1%2C%20and%20Apple%20iOS%20and%20iPadOS%20versions%20prior%20to%2016.7.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20vulnerability%20poses%20a%20significant%20threat%20as%20it%20allows%20remote%20attackers%20to%20execute%20arbitrary%20code%20on%20the%20targeted%20systems.%20The%20exploit%20leverages%20an%20out-of-bounds%20write%20issue%20in%20WebRTC%20and%20CoreMedia%2C%20enabling%20attackers%20to%20compromise%20devices%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20advisory%2C%20users%20of%20iPhone%20XS%2C%20iPad%20Pro%2012.9-inch%2C%20iPad%20Pro%2010.5-inch%2C%20iPad%20Pro%2011-inch%2C%20iPad%20Air%2C%20iPad%2C%20and%20iPad%20mini%20are%20susceptible%20if%20their%20devices%20are%20running%20iOS%20and%20iPadOS%20versions%20prior%20to%2017.4.1.%20Additionally%2C%20iPhone%208%2C%20iPhone%208%20Plus%2C%20iPhone%20X%2C%20iPad%205th%20generation%2C%20iPad%20Pro%209.7-inch%2C%20and%20iPad%20Pro%2012.9-inch%201st%20generation%20users%20are%20at%20risk%20if%20their%20devices%20are%20not%20updated%20to%20iOS%20and%20iPadOS%20versions%2016.7.7%20or%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacBook%20users%20are%20also%20urged%20to%20update%20their%20systems%2C%20with%20macOS%20Ventura%20versions%20prior%20to%2013.6.6%20and%20macOS%20Sonoma%20versions%20prior%20to%2014.4.1%20being%20vulnerable.%20Moreover%2C%20users%20of%20the%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%20headset%20should%20take%20note%20of%20the%20vulnerability%20in%20visionOS%20versions%20prior%20to%201.1.1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECERT-In%20recommends%20several%20precautionary%20measures%20to%20avoid%20the%20risk%20of%20compromise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsure%20that%20Apple%20iOS%2C%20iPadOS%2C%20macOS%2C%20and%20visionOS%20are%20updated%20to%20the%20latest%20versions%20containing%20security%20patches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetwork%20Security%3A%20Avoid%20connecting%20to%20unsecured%20or%20public%20Wi-Fi%20networks%20to%20minimize%20the%20risk%20of%20unauthorized%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnable%20Two-Factor%20Authentication%20(2FA)%3A%20Implement%202FA%20to%20add%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20security%20against%20potential%20credential%20compromises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDownload%20from%20Trusted%20Sources%3A%20Only%20download%20apps%20and%20software%20from%20reputable%20sources%20like%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%20to%20mitigate%20the%20risk%20of%20malware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegular%20Backups%3A%20Back%20up%20important%20data%20regularly%20to%20safeguard%20against%20data%20loss%20due%20to%20security%20breaches%20or%20system%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712139240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2Fs59joum8_apple-generic-reuters-650_625x300_30_October_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-issues-high-risk-warning-for-iphone-ipad-and-macbook-users-5365564%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Centre's%20security%20advisory%20from%20the%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(CERT-In)%20has%20issued%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh-risk%26quot%3B%20warning%20for%20users%20of%20Apple's%20iPhones%2C%20MacBooks%2C%20iPads%2C%20and%20Vision%20Pro%20headsets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-issues-high-risk-warning-for-iphone-ipad-and-macbook-users-5365564%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-issues-high-risk-warning-for-iphone-ipad-and-macbook-users-5365564%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-issues-high-risk-warning-for-iphone-ipad-and-macbook-users-5365564%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jonathan%20Glazer%20Donates%20Signed%20%E2%80%98Zone%20of%20Interest%E2%80%99%20Posters%20