ng%20almost%20four%20times%20the%20salary%20she%20earned%20as%20a%20teacher%20from%20influencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20abs%2C%20I%20was%20macro%20tracking%2C%20eating%20nuts%2C%20chicken%20and%20broccoli%20for%20meals%2C%20and%20went%20to%20the%20gym%20twice%20a%20day%2C%20an%20hour%20at%20a%20time%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20supposedly%20in%20the%20best%20shape%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20Aris%20was%20finding%20things%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20she%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcentral.gymshark.com%2Farticle%2Fsophie-aris-on-becoming-a-bikini-competitor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20blog%20post%20for%20Gymshark%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20challenges%20of%20bodybuilding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20simple%20fact%20is%20that%20competing%20is%20not%20for%20everyone%20and%20it's%20definitely%20not%20all%20glamour%2C%20roses%20and%20fairy%20tales%20like%20some%20are%20led%20to%20believe%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20tough%20both%20mentally%20and%20physically%20at%20times%20and%20difficult%20for%20those%20around%20you%20to%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAris%20said%20bodybuilding%20competitively%20meant%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20a%20social%20life%2C%20and%20dealing%20with%20the%20isolation%20of%20it%20being%20a%20very%20%26quot%3Bselfish%20sport.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20body%20dysmorphia%20to%20contend%20with%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20developing%20an%20unhealthy%20relationship%20with%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it's%20our%20body%20that%20is%20being%20judged%2C%20so%20naturally%2C%20we%20become%20more%20aware%20of%20every%20little%20imperfection%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bodybuilding%20industry%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbodybuilding-steroid-use-leads-to-deaths-s