t-we-know-about-the-seven-victims-of-grave-mistake-by-israeli-forces-13106948%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere%20Was%20A%20Time%20When%20PM%20Talked%20About%20China%20First%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20Nehru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20deliberations%20with%20his%20then-deputy%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20over%20a%20permanent%20seat%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20China%20got%20a%20place%20in%20the%20forum%20ahead%20of%20India%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20made%20the%20remarks%20during%20an%20address%20at%20the%20Gujarat%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20revealing%20how%20Sardar%20Patel%20warned%20PM%20Nehru%20of%20a%20threat%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20latter%20played%20down%20his%20concerns%20and%2C%20instead%2C%20advocated%20a%20permanent%20seat%20at%20the%20UNSC%20for%20China%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201950%2C%20there%20was%20an%20exchange%20of%20views%20between%20Sardar%20Patel%20and%20(Jawaharlal)%20Nehru...%20Sardar%20Patel%20had%20warned%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20about%20China.%20Sardar%20Patel%20said%20that%20today%2C%20we%20are%20facing%20a%20situation%20of%20two%20fronts%20(Pakistan%20and%20China)%20which%20for%20India%20has%20never%20happened%20in%20our%20history%20before.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20whatever%20the%20Chinese%20are%20saying%2C%20he%20feels%20that%20their%20intent%20is%20not%20good%20and%20therefore%20let%20us%20take%20precautions%2C%20let%20us%20build%20a%20policy%20around%20this.%20Nehru's%20position%20was...he%20was%20completely%20dissenting%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20Patel%20'you%20are%20unnecessarily%20suspicious%20of%20the%20Chinese.%20Also%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20anybody%20to%20attack%20us%20across%20the%20Himalayas.%20A%20few%20years%20later%2C%20there%20was%20a%20debate%20about%20the%20UN%2C%20should%20India%20be%20given%20a%20UN%20seat%20at%20that%20time%3F%20So%20Nehru's%20position%20at%20that%20time%20was%20he%20said%2C%20'we%20deserve%20a%20seat%2C%20but%20first%20we%20must%20ensure%20China%20gets%20a%20seat'.%20So%20today%20we%20are%20talking%20of%20India%20first.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20PM%20of%20India%20talked%20about%20China%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20weighed%20in%20on%20Sardar%20Patel's%20position%20of%20not%20taking%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Centre%2C%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20%26quot%3Bmany%20issues%20inherited%20from%20the%20past%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20I%20think%20people%20know%20that%20Sardar%20Patel%20was%20opposed%20to%20our%20going%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20because%20he%20knew%20the%20mentality%20of%20a%20judge%20there.%20So%20which%20coup%20will%20go%20to%20that%20point%3F%20It%20was%20like%20a%20common%20sense%20view%20he%20had.%20But%20yet%20we%20went%20and%20you%20know%2C%20once%20we%20went%20there%2C%20pressure%20was%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20military%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20our%20boundaries%2C%20our%20territories%2C%20some%20say%20rewrite%20our%20boundaries.%20Our%20boundaries%20are%20still%20our%20boundaries.%20We%20should%20never%20ever%20doubt%20that.%20But%20our%20problem%20today%20is%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20past.%20In%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20tried%20to%20deal%20with%20many%20issues%20inherited%20from%20the%20past%2C%20it%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20finding%20solutions%20to%20some%20of%20them%20while%20some%20issues%20will%20take%20more%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20to%20the%20UN%20on%20January%201%2C%201948%2C%20raising%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20at%20the%20world%20body%20over%20Pakistani%20infiltrators%20occupying%20parts%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20that%20had%20legally%20acceded%20to%20India%2C%20and%20demanding%20that%20they%20be%20asked%20to%20leave.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712129760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Fjim710t_jawaharlal-nehru_650x400_14_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-on-jawaharlal-nehru-there-was-a-time-when-pm-talked-about-china-first-5364479%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20deliberations%20with%20Sardar%20Patel%20over%20a%20permanent%20seat%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20China%20got%20a%20place%20in%20the%20forum%20ahead%20of%20India%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-on-jawaharlal-nehru-there-was-a-time-when-pm-talked-about-china-first-5364479%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-on-jawaharlal-nehru-there-was-a-time-when-pm-talked-about-china-first-5364479%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-on-jawaharlal-nehru-there-was-a-time-when-pm-talked-about-china-first-5364479%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vistara%20CEO%20To%20Meet%20Pilots%20Afte