ge.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20bull%20crap%20out%20there%20as%20well.%20You%20know%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20stories%20are%20just%20planted.%20A%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20just%20planted%20on%20other%20people's%20names%2C%20including%20my%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20communication%2C%20that%20clarity%20should%20have%20come%20out%20a%20little%20more%20for%20all%20this%20to%20die%20down.%20So%20it's%20not%20a%20case%20of%20you%20saying%2C%20'No%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C'%20or%20'He%20was%20treated%20badly%2C'%20and%20all%20the%20things%20that%20are%20coming%20out%20in%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShastri%20expects%20the%20tide%20to%20turn%20once%20Mumbai%20Indians%20start%20winning.%20The%20team%20is%20currently%20on%20a%20three-match%20losing%20streak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20my%20advice%20to%20Hardik%20would%20be%20to%20be%20calm%2C%20patient%2C%20ignore%2C%20and%20just%20focus%20on%20your%20game.%20Get%20a%20couple%20of%20performances%20going.%20Mumbai%20Indians%20is%20a%20terrific%20side.%20If%20they%20get%20on%20a%20roll%2C%20they%20win%20three%20or%20four%20matches%20on%20the%20trot%2C%20everything%20will%20subside%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712129580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fb0l6in_hardik-pandya-training-bcci_625x300_02_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fcrap-planted-stories-ravi-shastri-lifts-lid-on-conspiracy-against-hardik-pandya-5364794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravi%20Shastri%20advised%20Hardik%20Pandya%20to%20stay%20calm%20and%20weather%20the%20storm%20with%20solid%20performances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%