liedmarketresearch.com%2Findia-ready-to-eat-and-ready-to-cook-food-market-A47234%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520India%2520ready%252Dto%252Deat%2C17.6%2525%2520from%25202022%2520to%25202031.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98India%20Ready-To-Eat%20(RTE)%20and%20Ready-To-Cook%20(RTC)%20Food%20Market%20Size%2C%20Share%2C%20Competitive%20Landscape%20and%20Trend%20Analysis%20Report%20by%20Type%2C%20Product%2C%20Distribution%20Channel%20%3A%20Opportunity%20Analysis%20and%20Industry%20Forecast%2C%202022-2031%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20for%20Allied%20Market%20Research%20in%20November%202022%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711765229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345374%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founded%20by%20M%20S%20Ravindran%2C%20Nagarathna%20Ravindran%2C%20and%20Malathi%20Sharma%2C%20Adukale%20highlights%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Karnataka's%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20through%20ready-to-eat%20dishes%20like%20poha%2C%20gojjavalakki%20and%20bisi%20bele%20bath.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345374%2Ftraditional-karnataka-food-recipes-adukale-sankethi-cuisine-read-to-eat-poha-upma-bisi-bele-bath-sambar-powder%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98This%20Land%20is%20Their%20Home%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20a%20Filmmaker%20Fought%20Authorities%20to%20Protect%20Leopards%20In%20Rajasthan%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20do%20a%20quick%20Google%20search%20for%20%E2%80%98Leopard%20Country%E2%80%99%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20surprised%20when%20the%20result%20is%20not%20the%20name%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98country%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20map%2C%20but%20instead%20a%20small%20region%20in%20western%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hills%20of%20Jawai%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Pali%20district%20are%20home%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F127169%2Fhuman-leopard-conflict-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20population%20of%20leopards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thus%20earning%20the%20area%20this%20moniker.%20The%20ode%20will%20seem%20fitting%20as%20you%20scroll%20through%20the%20scenic%20images%20that%20accompany%20the%20search%20results.%20The%20outlining%20caves%20of%20Jawai%20are%20an%20idyllic%20home%20for%20the%20wild%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20interspersed%20among%20these%20pictures%20%E2%80%94%20some%20that%20showcase%20a%20leopard%20sitting%20idly%2C%20others%20that%20capture%20it%20taking%20a%20stroll%20%E2%80%94%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20a%20few%20surprising%20shots.%20One%20that%20caught%20my%20eye%20was%20a%20leopard%20in%20close%20quarters%20with%20a%20lone%20man%20herding%20his%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20country%20that%20wakes%20up%20to%20gory%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estories%20of%20leopards%3C%2Fa%3E%20attacking%20and%20mauling%20unfortunate%20humans%2C%20the%20sight%20is%20startling.%20A%20quick%20research%20spree%20led%20me%20to%20discover%20that%20these%20men%20were%20members%20of%20the%20Rabari%20community%20that%20moved%20to%20India%20from%20Iran%20a%20thousand%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20are%20distinguished%20by%20their%20attire%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20a%20red%20turban%20worn%20on%20the%20head%20with%20a%20white%20shirt%20that%20is%20tied%20in%20knots%20with%20strings.%20The%20look%20is%20completed%20with%20a%20floral%20print%20towel%20over%20their%20shoulder%20and%20shoes%20whose%20ends%20curl%20upwards.%20But%20the%20attire%20is%20not%20the%20only%20thing%20this%20nomadic%20pastoral%20community%20is%20famous%20for.%20They%20are%20also%20highly%20regarded%20for%20their%20harmonious%20relationship%20with%20the%20indigenous%20leopards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20will%20be%20well%20aware%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F264378%2Fkarma-sonam-natwest-group-earth-heroes-award-snow-leopard-himalayan-wolf-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleopard%20sightings%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20attacks%20have%20become%20increasingly%20common%20across%20the%20country.%20An%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20mentions%20that%20between%20January%202000%20and%20December%202023%2C%20a%20total%20of%20551%20fatal%20attacks%20were%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20then%20is%20the%20Rabari%20community%20managing%20to%20peacefully%20co-exist%20with%20the%20spotted%20wild%20cats%3F%20How%20do%20they%20go%20about%20their%20daily%20affairs%20without%20fear%2C%20in%20a%20region%20where%20the%20odds%20of%20crossing%20paths%20with%20the%20animal%20are%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201831px)%20100vw%2C%201831px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_4568_11zon-1710483143-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221831%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shatrunjay%20Pratap%20Singh%20is%20a%20filmmaker%20and%20conservation%20in%20Bera%2C%20Rajasthan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_4568_11zon-1710483143-scaled.jpeg%201831w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_4568_11zon-1710483143-215x300.jpeg%20215w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_4568_11zon-1710483143-500x699.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu