t%20advanced%20farming%20techniques%20such%20as%20hydroponics%2C%20microgreens%2C%20and%20indoor%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338349%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-with-aeroponics-online-classes-himachal-pradesh-solan-mushrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20really%20impressed%20by%20these%20experiences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20India%20imports%2070%20percent%20of%20saffron%20from%20Iran%20due%20to%20the%20limited%20availability%20within%20the%20country%2C%20and%20Kashmir%20only%20meets%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20domestic%20demands.%20This%20gap%20between%20demand%20and%20supply%20is%20a%20huge%20market%20in%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%2065-year-old%20engineer%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20saffron%20cultivation%20after%20his%20retirement.%20In%202017%2C%20he%20started%20growing%20saffron%20in%20a%20100-square-foot%20room%20in%20Sector%2063%2C%20Noida.%20He%20spent%20Rs%204%20lakh%20to%20construct%20a%20greenhouse%20to%20create%20a%20suitable%20environment%20to%20cultivate%20saffron%20within%20an%20artificial%20structure.%20He%20spent%20an%20additional%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20procure%20saffron%20seeds%20from%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsaffron-1711452013.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202017%2C%20Ramesh%20started%20growing%20saffron%20in%20a%20100-square-foot%20room%20in%20Noida.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsaffron-1711452013.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2